{"tid":93103,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[最新] 西甲半程MVP列表","createTime":"2017-01-24T07:01:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-24T12:58:17.000Z","uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"573bf5a4e2b41a860b21121b3be346fe83253107","tid":93103,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T07:01:41.000Z","msg":"今季西甲賽程剛剛過半，《馬卡報》組織讀者進行投票，選出了每支球隊的最佳球員，其中巴塞最佳球員是美斯，皇馬最佳球員為莫歷，基沙文則當選馬體會最佳球員。此外，日本名將乾貴士當選為埃瓦爾半程最佳。<br />\n<br />\n以下為各隊評選結果：<br />\n<br />\n　　艾拉維斯：帕切科<br />\n<br />\n　　畢巴：魯爾-加西亞<br />\n<br />\n　　馬體會：基沙文<br />\n<br />\n　　巴塞：美斯<br />\n<br />\n　　貝迪斯：魯文-卡斯特羅<br />\n<br />\n　　切爾達：阿斯帕斯<br />\n<br />\n　　拉科：安東內<br />\n<br />\n　<span style=\"color: red;\">　埃瓦爾：乾貴士</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n　　愛斯賓奴：迪亞高-洛佩斯<br />\n<br />\n　　格拉納達：卡沙爾拉<br />\n<br />\n　　拉斯彭馬斯：保定<br />\n<br />\n　　萊加內斯：希馬諾夫斯基<br />\n<br />\n　　馬拉加：辛度<br />\n<br />\n　　奧沙辛拿：沙治奧-利安<br />\n<br />\n　　皇馬：莫歷<br />\n<br />\n　　皇家蘇斯達：伊拿拉文迪<br />\n<br />\n　　西維爾：恩宗齊<br />\n<br />\n　　希杭：卡蒙拿<br />\n<br />\n　　華倫西亞：索萊爾<br />\n<br />\n　　維拉利爾：泰利哥斯贊"},{"pid":"d7e215190d4ff70d257e85d03b118eef8270c474","tid":93103,"uid":41093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T07:07:14.000Z","msg":"皇馬mvp唔係c朗已經唔洗睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不嬲都係c朗carry班垃圾"},{"pid":"886506563f04f3d48a8c37cc3b36a14feca63723","tid":93103,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T07:40:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2566e4f7aca165275f95412d57331470e0d5ac30","tid":93103,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T10:16:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f2e2ef683fe60f69cf15fd3633852be00e96deb","tid":93103,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T10:19:07.000Z","msg":"　切爾達：阿斯帕斯<br />\n<br />\n多謝紅軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14af52a3e8700e96e6bd00bac72940a3dd84e396","tid":93103,"uid":11252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T10:20:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>皇馬mvp唔係c朗已經唔洗睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不嬲都係c朗carry班垃圾</blockquote><br />\n戇鳩"},{"pid":"6787201084afe526a025792a3698d062c6a8ea88","tid":93103,"uid":2538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T10:26:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>　切爾達：阿斯帕斯<br />\n<br />\n多謝紅軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nispas朋友隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16011828b80f5732ca2fda0c2bbabd09ee4f4a21","tid":93103,"uid":2538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T10:27:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>皇馬mvp唔係c朗已經唔洗睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不嬲都係c朗carry班垃圾</blockquote><br />\n皇馬mvp點睇都係ramos<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e67fe454c05ac1aa4129de3448f40c14bdfb44e","tid":93103,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T10:32:49.000Z","msg":"d譯名乜撚事 邊個打邊個"},{"pid":"48cc773a4593261bcc3428e283573c2a1d263f86","tid":93103,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T10:34:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>皇馬mvp唔係c朗已經唔洗睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不嬲都係c朗carry班垃圾</blockquote><br />\n皇馬mvp點睇都係ramos<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n莫迪好勁喎 雖然<br />\n<br />\n進入到2017年以來，<span style=\"color: red;\">施丹的球隊在各條戰線的6場比賽中攻入了15粒入球</span>，但是來自於球隊鋒線的入球卻突然銳減，只有4粒入球，其中C.朗拿度和賓施馬各自攻入了兩粒入球，而莫拉達、華斯基斯以及馬里安奴費拉拿則沒有入球。<br />\n<br />\n而拉莫斯最近的火熱入球狀態則讓皇馬鋒線更加相形見絀，拉莫斯在2017年已經攻入了3粒入球，一個人就幾乎頂上了皇馬的整條鋒線。除了拉莫斯之外，華拉尼和馬些路在2017年也分別攻入1粒入球，也就是說在2017年，<span style=\"color: red;\">皇馬的後衛線承包了15粒入球中的5粒</span>，比前鋒線竟然還要多出1粒入球來。怎樣激活球隊的鋒線，真的需要施丹去想想主意了。"},{"pid":"fad1e13ca687e3d2e0fd054944fb2a771986fb4e","tid":93103,"uid":283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T10:34:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>皇馬mvp唔係c朗已經唔洗睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不嬲都係c朗carry班垃圾</blockquote><br />\n皇馬mvp點睇都係ramos<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n假膠都咁認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f55ae5d2932848bee38714c45088e3d89cf4fb6c","tid":93103,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T10:34:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>d譯名乜撚事 邊個打邊個</blockquote><br />\n有邊個睇唔明"},{"pid":"ed43ac2ee15c009f0cbf1a47477845e7e242b7ec","tid":93103,"uid":56377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T12:55:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3408e3cf39eddc0ac3e3ee132ead3c2157f891f7","tid":93103,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T12:57:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>d譯名乜撚事 邊個打邊個</blockquote><br />\n有邊個睇唔明</blockquote><br />\n日本仔邊隊"},{"pid":"935ea9b15ea5f453eddaddac520bcbff1dd53860","tid":93103,"uid":993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T12:58:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>d譯名乜撚事 邊個打邊個</blockquote><br />\n有邊個睇唔明</blockquote><br />\n日本仔邊隊</blockquote><br />\n伊巴"}]}